    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158430/extras/60de32f4afc228e5d7157cb5e9263228.poster.avif?t=1736806885\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158430/extras/60de32f4afc228e5d7157cb5e9263228.webm?t=1736806885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158430/extras/60de32f4afc228e5d7157cb5e9263228.mp4?t=1736806885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There was peace between humans, elves, dwarves and even orcs. As a lone wanderer, you try to find a place to camp in the forest. After you venturing deeper into the forest, you find a campsite. But deep in the dark forest, you never know what you might encounter.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158430/extras/579c7f82e888017a69f28335d95e2794.avif?t=1736806885\" width=600 height=192 /></span><br><br>You are kidnapped by an outcast tribe of orcs. As you learn why this tribe is abducting people, you'll try to escape the orc stronghold.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158430/extras/a98562c2c52f4fecf29a159ae7c3d979.avif?t=1736806885\" width=600 height=214 /></span><br><br>A retro survival horror adventure featuring:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore the stronghold to find a way out.<br></li><li>Uncover the story of an outcast tribe of orcs.<br></li><li>Find clues and solve puzzles.<br></li><li>Fight orcs to reach the exit.<br></li><li>Tank control as in retro survival horror classics.</li></ul>",
